51,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"回帶<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?&amp;v=4ttHc_a3ids\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3F%26v%3D4ttHc_a3ids&d=0skjTMQjnkPTMpFpIFFVW%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ab6a810e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?&amp;v=4ttHc_a3ids</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=5V40EbZOlok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5V40EbZOlok&d=0skjTMQjnkPTMpFpIFFVW%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=55841478\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=5V40EbZOlok</a>"},{"pid":"dd6999204eefc3e4eeebd4e56e733d32c8b173c9","tid":565651,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:59:36.000Z","msg":"關珮琳於1986年開始參與電影演出，以《八喜臨門》及《富貴逼人系列》的演出最為人知曉。她於1994年退出娛樂圈。<br />\n<br />\n網上有流傳說她在國泰廣告部任職、也有說她任職摩根大通，關珮琳表示之前的確在國泰公司任職，不過是做人力資源部門，負責飛機師的面試，在國泰任職十年後，她想趁年輕仍然有勇氣和衝勁向外闖時決定辭職，目前在一間跨國律師行同樣負責人力資源管理，當初選擇這個行業是因為她喜歡接觸人、與人溝通，這個行業不斷有機會學習新事物，未婚的她對目前的工作和生活都很滿意。<br />\n<br />\n關珮琳在2016年明報周刊2474期接受訪問透露2016年現職羅兵咸永道會計師事務所人力資源部，<br />\n<br />\n現在很多網民將內地超級女聲比賽參賽者謝雅雯的相片誤認為關珮琳。"},{"pid":"e2af4b9c12ae8afd1337d023b6fac92341660354","tid":565651,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:02:12.000Z","msg":"出身自台灣嘅童星黃坤玄，曾經同過周潤發（發哥）合作拍電影《阿郎的故事》，飾演發哥嘅仔仔「波仔」、佢又同過劉松仁合作過電影《愛的世界》，由於當時佢個樣勁得意，令人留下深刻印象。唔經唔覺黃坤玄依家已經39歲，佢喺2014年嗰陣罕有咁喺社交網甫文話：「03年拍完電視劇《金劍雕翎》後，演藝生涯也就基本到此結束了。」並表示感謝大家對佢一路嘅支持，及後黃坤玄都只係間唔中喺社交網更新近況。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直至前日，黃坤玄罕有喺社交網甫文留言話：「每次登上微博，總能看見大家給我許多的留言，令我剛到非常驚喜。謝謝你們，沒有忘記我。你們的每條信息，都讓我覺得如此溫馨。這些年來，我過得很好，希望你們也要健康快樂下去。心懷感恩！ 」"},{"pid":"6cd9789f1c3478532a3724e900266a27ee7b1de8","tid":565651,"uid":61967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:05:47.000Z","msg":"有無關佩琳近照?"},{"pid":"3065ba067afd6f8a2895b3229e4676f3748025dd","tid":565651,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無關佩琳近照?</blockquote><br />\n上面嗰張就係，2年前喺電影金像"},{"pid":"ff13382b0e35e4d73dc58ef867663c2eadcbd2a2","tid":565651,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無關佩琳近照?</blockquote><br />\n上面嗰張就係，2年前喺電影金像</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FG3L18cICG8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFG3L18cICG8&d=0skjTMQjnkPTMpFpIFFVW%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f4410881\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FG3L18cICG8</a><br />\n有得睇返<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97f0547e2f88d853869c09f03992ed7ca0a77ebb","tid":565651,"uid":3405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://9.share.photo.xuite.net/huangky/1958fe8/11363935/532442249_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F9.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fhuangky%2F1958fe8%2F11363935%2F532442249_m.jpg&h=fedd6efa&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://komicolle.dreamhosters.com/pix/img7208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkomicolle.dreamhosters.com%2Fpix%2Fimg7208.jpg&h=4a01ef65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8c865c8d3754f8ae2da551e3b47ce0bd193bcf9","tid":565651,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:48:51.000Z","msg":"黃坤玄喺藍色霹靂火又係大嗌老母老豆，好似阿郎收尾咁，有冇人睇過<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589